description: Quite simply put, I forked Bitcoin into its 69th chain primarily because I did not agree with the last 68 propositions and monetary philosophies. I use an X1000 hashing algorithm and it's also proof of armchair trolling. We start our ICO very soon and please be sure to send your investment into this anonymous address very soon. If you have problems with our pre-mining please refer to our ANN and we will gladly not answer any of your questions.
collection_description: SuperRare makes it easy to create, sell, and collect rare digital art. SuperRare's smart contract platform allows artists to release limited-edition digital artwork tracked on the blockchain, making the pieces rare, verified, and collectible. Filter the crypto art world's best selling works by artist name, creation type, and year of birth on OpenSea.
